{"tid":677392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：普教中教材驚現臭豬西西","createTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T07:30:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"070b999d3ce30f5ab472127837257c048805ba07","tid":677392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180525/20401126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F20401126&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSStr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8143191f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F20401126&h=f2b2a2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180525/20401126</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月25日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：普教中教材驚現臭豬西西<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180525/large/1527181317_6fec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180525%2Flarge%2F1527181317_6fec.jpg&h=786ae05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n正所謂「九聲六調」，廣東話千變萬化，冇可能同普通話互通，真係有辦你睇。有本疑似普教中教科書，故事入面幫隻豬改名叫做西西，仲要唔沖涼又臭㖭，可能喺大陸人眼中一個得意可愛小豬故事，嚟到香港就變咗其他嘢，所以話普教中喺香港，係咪真係可行呢？<br />\n<br />\n網上瘋傳嘅呢個課本故事，內容係話「西西是頭小豬，一頭不肯洗澡、臭哄哄的小豬。有一天，臭豬西西要去旅行，他匆匆從牆上掛鈎取下帽子，看了一眼掛鐘，就出發了。<br />\n<br />\n半路上，一輛車從臭豬西西的身旁開過，臭豬西西悄悄地跳上後面的掛車，得意極了！」你唔好理咩叫「掛車」先，淨係「臭豬西西」已經令到一眾巴絲一路睇一路笑，既然大家咁好學，我哋就走去search吓咩叫掛車，原來係指車斗咁解，唔係指臭豬西西喺架車度「掛掉」（死）呀！  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：拖頭跌鐵板　累紅隧大塞車<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n19歲仔登珠峯頂相有得睇！拎埋香港旗好架勢"},{"pid":"2a490d167ce57b40faee4aa9e2877ce53f32327f","tid":677392,"uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"加多個「小娜猩猩」"},{"pid":"5c4c8f137837162ea549a80abe56b724210fc6cb","tid":677392,"uid":9231,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a490d167ce57b40faee4aa9e2877ce53f32327f","tid":677392,"uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"加多個「小娜猩猩」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"ffde27a869c67c2ebc5575789c1804f5db9ff31c","tid":677392,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa56bf1d4ebecca5cc264dbe27354139e6b90b09","tid":677392,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3bb75d9a510dc7b2a2d944d09dda008dbd46341","tid":677392,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9009fede59403db5ede3f72e11a88d275996e7","tid":677392,"uid":55093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffde27a869c67c2ebc5575789c1804f5db9ff31c","tid":677392,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"普教中=普通話教中文<br />\n唔係普通話教中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b473befb763ed54ce8172ce40d86c167ac28f07","tid":677392,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"臭豬閪閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5051402218f1655a581d8298972c281b928d1b2d","tid":677392,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a490d167ce57b40faee4aa9e2877ce53f32327f","tid":677392,"uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"加多個「小娜猩猩」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse